Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:30.21,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine Twice
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:32.34,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,像在哭泣的Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.38,0:23:34.01,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也会心烦
